import React from 'react'
import { Card, Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
const Blog = ({ blog }) => {
  console.log(blog)
  return (
    <Card border="primary" style={{ width: '80rem', margin: '15px' }}>
      <Card.Header>Author :{blog.author}</Card.Header>
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Title: {blog.title}</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>{blog.name}</Card.Text>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default Blog
